---
layout: layouts/default.njk
title: Music
---

{% macro youtube(item) %}
  <article class="w-full md:w-4/5 mx-auto mb-16">
    <header class="mb-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif">{{ item.name }}</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="youtube-container">
      <iframe title="{{ item.title }}" class="youtube" src="{{ item.url }}" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>
  </article>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro bandcamp(item) %}
  <article class="w-full md:w-4/5 mx-auto mb-16">
    <header class="mb-3">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif">{{ item.name }}</h2>
      {% if item.artist %}<div class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">by {{ item.artist }}</div>{% endif %}
    </header>
    <iframe title="{{ item.title }}" style="border: 0; width: 100%; height: 274px;" src="https://bandcamp.com/EmbeddedPlayer/album={{ item.album }}/size=large/bgcol=ffffff/linkcol=0687f5/artwork=small/transparent=true/" seamless>
      <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.name }}</a>
    </iframe>
  </article>
{% endmacro %}

<div>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif mb-4">Music</h1>
  <p class="mb-10">
    Music is an integral part of my life. I started playing piano when I was little, and have played many different instruments in many different bands since then.
    I find that very often the creativity and problem solving involved in music making for me is very similar in essence to software development, which is why I enjoy the two.
    Here are a few recordings of music I created or had a part in making.
  </p>

  {% for item in music %}
    {% if item.type == "youtube" %}
      {{ youtube(item) }}
    {% elif item.type == "bandcamp" %}
      {{ bandcamp(item) }}
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</div>
